scripts.postpublish: git push && git push --tags && cd ../d3.github.com && git pull && cp ../d3/dist/d3.js d3.v${npm_package_version%%.*}.js && cp ../d3/dist/d3.min.js d3.v${npm_package_version%%.*}.min.js && git add d3.v${npm_package_version%%.*}.js d3.v${npm_package_version%%.*}.min.js && git commit -m "d3 ${npm_package_version}" && git push && cd - && zip -j dist/d3.zip -- LICENSE README.md API.md CHANGES.md dist/d3.js dist/d3.min.js
scripts.pretest: rimraf dist && mkdir dist && json2module package.json > dist/package.js && rollup -c
